&lt;h2&gt;How to Add a Job&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="how-to-add-a-job"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#how-to-add-a-job" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-steps hx:ml-4 hx:mb-12 hx:ltr:border-l hx:rtl:border-r hx:border-gray-200 hx:ltr:pl-6 hx:rtl:pr-6 hx:dark:border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Go to the Job List&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="go-to-the-job-list"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#go-to-the-job-list" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tap the &lt;strong&gt;Jobs Tab&lt;/strong&gt; at the bottom. This will take you to the &lt;strong&gt;Job List&lt;/strong&gt; for the Current Crew Member.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-01.webp"
alt="Go to the Job List" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tap the &amp;lsquo;Add Job&amp;rsquo; Button&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="tap-the-add-job-button"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#tap-the-add-job-button" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tap the &lt;strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;+&amp;rsquo; Button&lt;/strong&gt; in the top right. This will show the &lt;strong&gt;Add New Job Screen&lt;/strong&gt;. This is where you set the Job Name, Production Company, Role, Department, Rate and Job Settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-02.webp"
alt="Tap the &amp;#39;Add Job&amp;#39; Button" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Enter Job Name and Production Company&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="enter-job-name-and-production-company"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#enter-job-name-and-production-company" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;You must enter a &lt;strong&gt;Job Name&lt;/strong&gt;. Select a &lt;strong&gt;Production Company&lt;/strong&gt; from the list. Tap the &lt;strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;+&amp;rsquo; Button&lt;/strong&gt; in the toolbar to Add a New Production Company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-03.webp"
alt="Enter Job Name and Production Company" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-2 hx:ltr:pr-4 hx:rtl:pl-4 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-blue-200 hx:bg-blue-100 hx:text-blue-900 hx:dark:border-blue-200/30 hx:dark:bg-blue-900/30 hx:dark:text-blue-200"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:ltr:pl-3 hx:ltr:pr-2 hx:rtl:pr-3 hx:rtl:pl-2"&gt;&lt;svg height=1.2em class="hx:inline-block hx:align-middle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:w-full hx:min-w-0 hx:leading-7"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production Companies&lt;/strong&gt; are referred to as &lt;strong&gt;Clients&lt;/strong&gt; in the Invoice Section of Crew Call.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Modify Role, Department or Rate If Required&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="modify-role-department-or-rate-if-required"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#modify-role-department-or-rate-if-required" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;These will be pre-filled based on the defaults in your &lt;strong&gt;Crew Profile&lt;/strong&gt;. The most common value to modify is your rate as it&amp;rsquo;s likely you negotiate this on a job to job basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-04.webp"
alt="Modify Role, Department or Rate If Required" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Add Job&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="add-job"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#add-job" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tap the &lt;strong&gt;Add Button&lt;/strong&gt; in the bottom right. This will create a &lt;strong&gt;New Job&lt;/strong&gt; and add it to the &lt;strong&gt;Job List&lt;/strong&gt; for the Current Crew Member.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-05.webp"
alt="Add Job" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Editing Jobs</title><link>/docs/jobs/editing-jobs/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/jobs/editing-jobs/</guid><description>
&lt;h2&gt;How to Edit a Job&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="how-to-edit-a-job"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#how-to-edit-a-job" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-steps hx:ml-4 hx:mb-12 hx:ltr:border-l hx:rtl:border-r hx:border-gray-200 hx:ltr:pl-6 hx:rtl:pr-6 hx:dark:border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Go to the Job List&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="go-to-the-job-list"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#go-to-the-job-list" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tap the &lt;strong&gt;Jobs Tab&lt;/strong&gt; at the bottom. This will take you to the &lt;strong&gt;Job List&lt;/strong&gt; for the Current Crew Member.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/adding-jobs-05.webp"
alt="Go to the Job List" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Select &amp;lsquo;Edit Job&amp;rsquo;&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="select-edit-job"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#select-edit-job" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tap and Hold&lt;/strong&gt; on a Job. Select &lt;strong&gt;Edit Job&lt;/strong&gt; from the menu.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/editing-jobs-01.webp"
alt="Select &amp;#39;Edit Job&amp;#39;" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Job Info&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="job-info"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#job-info" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can change the Job Name, Production Company, Role, Department or Rate. You can also mark jobs as Sent, Lock or Paid.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/editing-jobs-02.webp"
alt="Job Info" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-2 hx:ltr:pr-4 hx:rtl:pl-4 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-blue-200 hx:bg-blue-100 hx:text-blue-900 hx:dark:border-blue-200/30 hx:dark:bg-blue-900/30 hx:dark:text-blue-200"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:ltr:pl-3 hx:ltr:pr-2 hx:rtl:pr-3 hx:rtl:pl-2"&gt;&lt;svg height=1.2em class="hx:inline-block hx:align-middle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:w-full hx:min-w-0 hx:leading-7"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0"&gt;When you change your &lt;strong&gt;Rate&lt;/strong&gt; for a Job and select &lt;strong&gt;Save&lt;/strong&gt;, every Work Day for that Job will be re-calculated using the new rate.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Job Settings&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="job-settings"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#job-settings" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Overtime Calculations, Overtime Rules, Night Loadings, Meal Penalties and Turnarounds can be modified on a job to job basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are working on a different scale of production or in a different country, you may want to change these so that your income is calculated correctly for that specific job.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="image-frame"&gt;&lt;img src="/images/editing-jobs-03.webp"
alt="Job Settings" width="250"&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-2 hx:ltr:pr-4 hx:rtl:pl-4 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-blue-200 hx:bg-blue-100 hx:text-blue-900 hx:dark:border-blue-200/30 hx:dark:bg-blue-900/30 hx:dark:text-blue-200"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:ltr:pl-3 hx:ltr:pr-2 hx:rtl:pr-3 hx:rtl:pl-2"&gt;&lt;svg height=1.2em class="hx:inline-block hx:align-middle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:w-full hx:min-w-0 hx:leading-7"&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0"&gt;When you change any of the &lt;strong&gt;Calculations&lt;/strong&gt; and select &lt;strong&gt;Save&lt;/strong&gt;, every Work Day for that Job will be re-calculated using the new &lt;strong&gt;Job Settings&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>